Make sure you cd the src folder
then run the following commands in the terminal:
javac *.java (to compile)
java Main (to run)

Use wasd keys to move the turtle
w:up, a:left, s:down, d:right
Click on the mouse to shoot in that direction
Press the spacebar to pause the game
Press the play again button to play a new game

User wants to get the highest score possible


